# Drishti AI - Comprehensive Project Guide and Walkthrough

This document serves as a complete, guided walkthrough of the **Drishti-full** project. It is designed to help you deeply understand the entire architecture, the specific AI models used, and how data flows through the system. You can use this guide as the foundation for your presentation.

